Class StandardLabelIndex<T extends Label>

  • edu.umn.nlpengine.StandardLabelIndex<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LabelIndex<T>

    public class StandardLabelIndex<T extends Label>
implements LabelIndex<T>

    A label index backed by a immutable sorted array of interface TextRange values.
